Description: Soplos Welcome Live 2.0
 The world's most advanced welcome application for Soplos Linux Live Environment.
 .
 Features include:
  * Complete internationalization support for 8 languages
  * Advanced CHROOT recovery system with intelligent partition detection
  * Automatic XDG folders migration when changing language
  * NumLock management integration
  * GParted integration for disk management
  * Automatic locale and keyboard layout configuration
  * Real-time Python cache cleanup
  * Robust filesystem validation for CHROOT operations
  * Professional UI with keyboard mnemonics support
 .
 This application helps users navigate the live system, configure
 system settings, perform installations via Calamares, and recover
 installed systems using advanced CHROOT functionality.
Homepage: https://soplos.org
